      <title>瑞穗将与主权财富基金 PIF 合作推出沙特阿拉伯 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/mizuho-to-launch-saudi-arabia-etf-with-sovereign-wealth-fund-pif</link>
